  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Hubble's Law
Formula: v = H₀ × d
Note:    Universe is expanding; galaxies recede from us

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Euler's Identity
Formula: e^(iπ) + 1 = 0
Note:    Relates five fundamental constants; called most beautiful equation

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Speed of Light
Formula: c = 299,792,458 m/s in vacuum
Note:    Foundation of special relativity; universal speed limit

